<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-14618 AND RTLO-16618
        SERIES - REMOVE - SLAVE VALVE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="4">
        <title>SLAVE VALVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the four retaining bolts and the slave valve from the transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301920">Figure 20</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301920" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301920" filename="../figg13/G1301920.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 20. Remove Slave Valve From Transmission Case</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the hat-type alignment sleeve from the bore in slave valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301921">Figure 21</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301921" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301921" filename="../figg13/G1301921.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 21. Remove Hat-Type Alignment Sleeve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the spring and plunger pin from bore in the transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301922">Figure 22</hotlnk>). Remove slave valve gasket.
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301922" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301922" filename="../figg13/G1301922.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 22. Remove Spring and Plunger Pin</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If necessary, remove the air line fittings from the slave valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301923">Figure 23</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301923" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301923" filename="../figg13/G1301923.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 23. Remove Air Line Fittings From Slave Valve</caption>
            </figure>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>See disassembly and reassembly of piston-type
                        <hotlnk document="s13019_12.xml" xrefid="hl1301907">SLAVE VALVES
                            <xref refid="hl1301907"/>
                        </hotlnk>
                        .
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
